---
title: Shrimp & Spinach Ricotta Ravioli with Roasted Bell Pepper
description: Tender pasta pillows are good in any form, but they’re *especially* good when packed with spinach and ricotta. Add tender strips of roasted bell pepper and a cheesy garlic cream sauce to the mix and you’ve got yourself a winning dinner. Luckily, this elegant pasta is as easy to make as it is delicious. All you need is 35 minutes for this dish to hit your table.
